channel.title: Something weird at tele commands
channel.description:
Well... I was testing my server with a friend, if him or I use a teleport command, he can't see me. If I reset my server, then he sees me. Help?
Thanks in advance.
Kind Regards, Robin (Robintje1)
PS. I'm not using delta. PS². It's with EVERY teleport command.
